POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### SSO Login (Exchange Microsoft Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/sso
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ms_access_token": "{{msToken}}"
}
